<paragraph base="IFRS2020-5" id="IFRS16_BC267B" principles="no"><paranum>BC267B</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="BC267B"/></prolog><body><p>In developing the Phase 2 amendments, the Board also considered the potential effects of the reform on the financial statements of an entity applying the requirements of IFRS Standards, other than <xref href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_TOC.dita#IFRS09_TOC0001" scope="local"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IFRS 9</ph></ph></xref> and <xref href="../ias39/IAS39_TOC.dita#IAS39_TOC" scope="local"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IAS 39</ph></ph></xref>. The Board specifically considered the potential effects arising in the context of <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IFRS 16</ph></ph>.</p></body></paragraph>